name: born = Architects()
description: There is no translation to their name. For this reason, they are called Architects. They came from the stars. They walked this planet long before the first humans descended from the trees and left, before the first signs of intelligence began to appear in our heads. All that was left of them were granodiorite stelae and the inscriptions too complicated to decipher. However, we were able to understand the paintings. That was enough for us to never stop looking at the night sky without fear.
